					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">There are six combinations of two colors. This means each tile can be compressed into 11 bytes without any run-length or Huffman techniques: 8 bytes for the bits and 3 bytes for each 8x1 pixel sliver's colors.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

